57/*******************************************************************************
58 *
59 * FUNCTION: AcpiAhGetTableInfo
60 *
61 * PARAMETERS: Signature - ACPI signature (4 chars) to match
62 *
63 * RETURN: Pointer to a valid AH_TABLE. Null if no match found.
64 *
65 * DESCRIPTION: Find a match in the "help" table of supported ACPI tables
66 *
67 ******************************************************************************/
68
69const AH_TABLE *
70AcpiAhGetTableInfo (
71 char *Signature)
72{
73 const AH_TABLE *Info;
74
75
76 for (Info = AcpiGbl_SupportedTables; Info->Signature; Info++)
77 {
78 if (ACPI_COMPARE_NAMESEG (Signature, Info->Signature))
79 {
80 return (Info);
81 }
82 }
83
84 return (NULL);
85}
